{"tid":1165984,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Microsoft微軟網店下架華為手提電腦","createTime":"2019-05-22T07:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-22T11:26:29.000Z","uid":184679,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fe17b779668edfe1a4a2b3766bbb74b1ca89a9f0","tid":1165984,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T07:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20190522/_2019052214331254495.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20190522%2F_2019052214331254495.jpg&h=861fe10c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼美國商務部將華為及旗下68家附屬事業，列入有貿易黑名單 後，Google 決定停止授權 Android 系統與 Google 服務給華為。最新一間科技企業微軟（Microsoft）也有跟進行動。<br />\n<br />\n據《Business Insider》報道，雖然有現貨可以供應，但微軟上周末從網上商店中刪除了華為手提電腦Matebook，也引發該公司是否計劃阻止華為手提電腦的Windows 10更新的疑慮。<br />\n<br />\n由於華為的所有手提電腦都在Windows操作系統上運作，因此若微軟不再將其軟體和其他產品授權給華為，可能嚴重影響華為的手提電腦業務。<br />\n<br />\n另外微軟可能是因為安全漏洞而有此舉措。今年1月美國微軟在華為手提電腦發現一項安全性漏洞，研究人員在華為Matebook手提電腦發現後門。但當時微軟向華為回報此缺陷後，華為已迅速對軟件進行修補。<br />\n<br />\n微軟目前尚未就其與華為的關係發表官方聲明，但也不願意證實微軟將阻止華為手提電腦的Windows 10更新，僅簡短表示「我們沒有什麼可分享的」。<br />\n<br />\n由於禁令緣故，英特爾（Intel）、高通（Qualcomm）、博通（Broadcom）和賽靈思（Xilinx）等美國晶片製造商已告知員工，將停止向華為供貨。至於微軟是否成為下一家圍堵華為的廠商，仍有待觀察。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1505821/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1505821%2F&d=ruuHvkpDPTXA%2B6q4k3%2F6TU9C3ZeEg%2BAMpIxt97RLrpY%3D&h=c1c6ef12\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fwo%2F1505821%2F&h=29d6461a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/wo/1505821/</a>"},{"pid":"d45b847022400425f9576ba07df9bc89868c2cf3","tid":1165984,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7a88f71f34b8e216092a987690a6384918b5231","tid":1165984,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T09:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f4f6a6b3199e53090c534c03f6b948834de8f99","tid":1165984,"uid":27038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-22T11:26:29.000Z","msg":"唔好俾佢停丫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}